                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210912-148-off861 t18210912-148-crimeloc863"></join>, I saw three boys playing with a flour sack; I passed them a short distance, and then my baby had a pull at the neck - I turned round and caught the prisoner at my shoulder with the beads in his hand - he had taken them off the child's neck. He ran away - I am sure he is the boy.</p>
